PrecisReappointment of MARTHA HYNNA, of Ottawa, Ontario, as a member of the Advisory Committee on the Public Service Superannuation Act for a term ending March 1, 1999; appointment of MARTHA HYNNA, of Ottawa, Ontario, as Chairperson of the Advisory Committee on the Public Service Superannuation Act for a term ending March 1, 1999; reappointment of DARYL BEAN, of Nepean, Ontario; CLAUDE EDWARDS, of Ottawa, Ontario; SUSAN GIAMPIETRI, of Nepean, Ontario; JAMES LIVINGSTON, of Lake Charlotte, Nova Scotia; LAURA M. TALBOT-ALLAN, of Ottawa, Ontario; DARRELL TINGLEY, of Orleans, Ontario; and GARY MYERS, of Nepean, Ontario, as members of that Committee for a term ending March 1, 1999; and appointment of DAVEY J.T. LEWIS, of Gloucester, Ontario; YVONNE MONGEON, of Ottawa, Ontario; ROBERT M. EMOND, of Ottawa, Ontario; and STEVEN J. HINDLE, of Embrun, Ontario, as members of that Committee for a term ending March 1, 1999.
